channel.title: Can't log in to a server? Can't use Hamachi? Look here!
channel.description:
Alright, the main reason why I posted this is because there's a lot of topics asking this. So just to clarify why and what you do if you can't log in read here. Also if you don't know how to use Hamachi, this is the thread for you.
[b][u]FAQ's[/u][/b] Q: "OMG! WHY CAN'T I LOG IN TO ANY SERVER????!!!!!" A: The server's probably down for coding, even just re-starting. Keep on trying. Q: "ALL THE NO-IP SERVERS AREN'T WORKING?!!!!!!!!!!!!!" A: They will work, if you get to stressed out about it download Hamachi[url=http://hamachi.cc] here[/url]. *I'll post pictures on how to work Hamachi once you've downloaded it later on.* Q: "Why do I keep on being kicked of a server?!" A: You might of been massing so a Mod or Admin kicked you. If not just keep on trying to log in, as I've said before it just might of been restarted.
[b][u]Hamachi[/u][/b] In this part of the thread I'll show you the right way to use Hamachi. I'm not going to show you how to download it, you should know.
Step 1 - Once you've downloaded Hamachi, go to the new server status page by clicking[url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/serverstatus.php] here.[/url]
Step 2 - Click on Hamachi servers like the picture shows. [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img214.imageshack.us/img214/4594/step1hamachitj6.png[/img][/URL] Step 3 - Click on any one you want, I.E fr33sc4p3 pkz22. Then this should come up. Remember the IP! [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img405.imageshack.us/img405/3319/step2hamachipngdz4.png[/img][/URL] Step 4 - Open up Hamachi and join a server like this. [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img470.imageshack.us/img470/7052/step3hamachihz7.png[/img][/URL] Step 5 - Then. [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img405.imageshack.us/img405/7286/step4hamachibt9.png[/img][/URL] Step 6 - Open up MoparScape enter the server's IP. (See Step 3) And join the server!
Thanks for using my guide, I hope I've helped some people! =D Post your comments! =D
~ 99
